{"tid":2304143,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"✩奈奈分析日誌 ★ -數浪驚覺十年牛市已結束▁ ▂ ▃","createTime":"2020-11-28T13:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T02:26:47.000Z","uid":117947,"like":136,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"95d47e7b70c59a8cdc3d328fc6fa76a5d4317625","tid":2304143,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"xx-large\">嗱, 聲明先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n純粹個人分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係教人野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦唔構成任何投資買賣建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下分析會結合到<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">波浪理論</span><br />\n <span class=\"blue\">3角形理論</span><br />\n <span class=\"green\">江思理論</span><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">奈奈牛熊畫圖理論</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n我會盡量做個小總結, <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等新手都簡單易明每個部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先帶大家數下浪先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1GHDhk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1GHDhk.png&h=d76bbcc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛12345ABC已經出晒<br />\n估計十年牛市已經行完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(散戶豬豬發問): 咁係咪熊市啦<br />\n我地睇番下一個浪<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><strong> (圖中GAY佬粉背景</strong></span>黑色數字1既位置)<br />\n係升呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[url][/url]<br />\n由此估計, 十年牛市已經行完<br />\n接下來將會迎接下一個十年牛市<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:咁熊市呢?<br />\n而家改左行廿年牛市掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結論: 升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n數完浪,帶大家睇下3角形<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RSvNc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RSvNc0.png&h=e458ad3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n見唔見, 已經突破左3角形啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結論: 升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再睇番江恩理論<br />\n唔明可自行GOOGLE<br />\n不過奈奈都好貼心豬豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經搵埋書喂埋大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYb8yTT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYb8yTT.jpg&h=6ec2d19c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oynWHNf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoynWHNf.jpg&h=afc9b827&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因家貧買唔起量角尺<br />\n幾經辛苦老立左個o靚仔既三角尺同量角尺<br />\n去驗證呢條45度線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3c0JnNR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3c0JnNR.jpg&h=df830ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVsWHNT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVsWHNT.jpg&h=14069676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由此可見, 而家個趨勢係升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結論: 升升升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後奈奈畫左張圖做總結<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAjVdUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCAjVdUZ.jpg&h=7e3cf2ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab08084aa88616a6bbc41dfea6f7a1d189c35486","tid":2304143,"uid":227698,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"最後隻熊熊好搞笑"},{"pid":"f72fd6141ce92df1f4dc274f200989dc2efebcfa","tid":2304143,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab08084aa88616a6bbc41dfea6f7a1d189c35486","tid":2304143,"uid":227698,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"最後隻熊熊好搞笑"},"citedBy"